# Network Flow Diagram (Mermaid)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant CF as CloudFront
  participant W as AWS WAF
  participant LB as AWS LB
  participant N as Nginx Ingress
  participant A as OpenEdX App
  participant D as External Data Services

  U->>CF: HTTPS request (lms.blackmode.io)
  CF->>W: Forward request
  W->>LB: Allowed request
  LB->>N: HTTP/HTTPS upstream
  N->>A: Route to LMS/CMS service
  A->>D: Query MySQL/Mongo/Redis/OpenSearch
  D-->>A: Response
  A-->>N: App response
  N-->>LB: Upstream response
  LB-->>CF: Origin response
  CF-->>U: Cached/forwarded response
```

